LINSPIRE 5.1.427
================

Linspire is a Debian-based Linux operating system, which uses the popular Ubuntu Linux OS for its baseline.
Linspire starts with Ubuntu, then adds many additional features and software applications including proprietary software, codecs and drivers to provide you the world&#039;s easiest Linux-based operating system designed for laptop & desktop PCs.

With CNR, you have access to over 20,000 free & commercial software programs, packages and libraries.
